  Update Model Permissions

› 1. Default      FreeChaOS can read and edit files in the current workspace,
                  and run commands. Approval is required to access the
                  internet or edit other files.
  2. Full Access  FreeChaOS can edit files outside this workspace and access
                  the internet without asking for approval. Exercise caution
                  when using.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
